Tomorrow’s Guardian Life magazine has something really special in store for its readers.  If you’re a frequent traveller or plan to go on a vacation soon, then you’d find it even more interesting. Airplane passenger. Photo: New York Amsterdam News Guardian Life will be releasing a Travel edition tomorrow with unbiased recommendations for Nigerian travellers and tourists interested in visiting our country. Tailored to suit the needs of travellers in any country, you will get insider tips on how to plan the perfect summer escape, everything you need for your summer 2018 exploring and much more! The best part about tomorrow’s edition is that it will have a promo code to take N10,000 off your next flight for everyone who buys the issue. So be sure to grab a copy of your own as soon as you can.